  {
    "text": "is the winner.",
    "start": 143.57,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we go.",
    "start": 144.53,
    "duration": 0.66
  },
  {
    "text": "The real Team Coby\nfans realize I've won",
    "start": 154.37,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "many a mini battle in my life.",
    "start": 156.14,
    "duration": 1.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Which means nothing!",
    "start": 158.0,
    "duration": 3.16
  },
  {
    "text": "No one care more about\nmini battles than this guy.",
    "start": 161.16,
    "duration": 3.745
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, be honest, did you\njust watermelon-punt it?",
    "start": 170.13,
    "duration": 2.58
  },
  {
    "text": "He watermelon-punted?",
    "start": 172.71,
    "duration": 2.286
  },
  {
    "text": "Absolutely!",
    "start": 174.996,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "It's a great punt style.",
    "start": 175.496,
    "duration": 1.954
  },
  {
    "text": "That's just, folks that's sad.",
    "start": 177.45,
    "duration": 1.49
  },
  {
    "text": "This is the World's\nLongest Crossbar Hit.",
    "start": 184.25,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!",
    "start": 194.214,
    "duration": 0.982
  },
  {
    "text": "Woo!",
    "start": 195.196,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Time for a twin shot.",
    "start": 200.64,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "First, I hit my\ntarget, which releases",
    "start": 201.6,
    "duration": 1.71
