  {
    "text": "This is the Twin Tire Buster.",
    "start": 206.44,
    "duration": 1.37
  },
  {
    "text": "That's nice.",
    "start": 222.17,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Honestly, the laziest trick\nshot I could think of.",
    "start": 223.37,
    "duration": 2.185
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, as we wait,\nlet's enjoy another trick",
    "start": 225.555,
    "duration": 2.285
  },
  {
    "text": "shot from Ty.",
    "start": 227.84,
    "duration": 2.26
  },
  {
    "text": "The white balloon is the target.",
    "start": 230.1,
    "duration": 2.09
  },
  {
    "text": "This is Threading the Needle.",
    "start": 232.19,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Bang!",
    "start": 236.929,
    "duration": 1.491
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's go!",
    "start": 238.42,
    "duration": 0.994
  },
  {
    "text": "What a shot, T. Man,\nthose are fun to watch.",
    "start": 242.4,
    "duration": 2.55
  },
  {
    "text": "Anyways, my turn.",
    "start": 244.95,
    "duration": 3.636
  },
  {
    "text": "[CHEERING]",
    "start": 248.586,
    "duration": 2.293
  },
  {
    "text": "Like I said, laziest trick\nshot I could think of.",
    "start": 250.879,
    "duration": 2.041
  },
  {
    "text": "That was fun.",
    "start": 252.92,
    "duration": 1.01
  },
  {
    "text": "We got three dominoes.",
    "start": 257.129,
    "duration": 1.671
  },
  {
    "text": "Cody's going to be driving\nthe golf cart on the back,",
    "start": 258.8,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "he throws, hits the\nfirst domino, boom, hits",
    "start": 261.2,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "the second domino, boom,\nhits the third domino,",
    "start": 263.6,
    "duration": 2.67
