  {
    "text": "smashes the lever.",
    "start": 266.27,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, OK.",
    "start": 267.23,
    "duration": 0.609
  },
  {
    "text": "Launching the skeet in\nthe air, hopefully I",
    "start": 267.839,
    "duration": 1.791
  },
  {
    "text": "hit it before it hits\nthe ground and breaks.",
    "start": 269.63,
    "duration": 1.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Bang!",
    "start": 281.897,
    "duration": 0.994
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's go.",
    "start": 282.891,
    "duration": 1.988
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, buddy!",
    "start": 284.879,
    "duration": 0.994
  },
  {
    "text": "It's hard driving\nthese guys, you know?",
    "start": 289.195,
    "duration": 1.625
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh my god.",
    "start": 294.145,
    "duration": 0.95
  },
  {
    "text": "Have you lost your mind?",
    "start": 295.095,
    "duration": 1.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Upon further review, Ty\nand Coby are so close,",
    "start": 300.57,
    "duration": 3.54
  },
  {
    "text": "in the event that they're\ntied in the final,",
    "start": 304.11,
    "duration": 2.421
  },
  {
    "text": "they'll do a punt-off.",
    "start": 306.531,
    "duration": 1.884
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, quick update,\nwith Corey's touchback,",
    "start": 314.08,
    "duration": 2.14
  },
  {
    "text": "that means inside the\nfive is wide open,",
    "start": 316.22,
    "duration": 1.989
  },
  {
    "text": "let's put the ball there.",
    "start": 318.209,
    "duration": 1.041
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, Cobes and I finished\nnear the goal line.",
    "start": 326.62,
    "duration": 2.68
  },
  {
    "text": "We did.",
    "start": 329.3,
    "duration": 0.762
  },
  {
    "text": "Obviously, I don't\nwant to win like that.",
    "start": 330.062,
    "duration": 1.708
  },
  {
    "text": "So we're going to\ngo to a punt-off.",
    "start": 331.77,
    "duration": 0.99
  },
  {
    "text": "That's convenient, because I\ndon't want to win like that.",
    "start": 332.76,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "So we're going to do a punt-off.",
    "start": 334.24,
    "duration": 0.91
  },
  {
    "text": "I would have given\nit to Ty anyways,",
    "start": 335.15,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "because he didn't\nwatermelon-kick it.",
    "start": 336.13,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
    "start": 337.69,
    "duration": 1.723
  },
  {
    "text": "[BELL CHIMING]",
    "start": 345.666,
    "duration": 0.962
  },
  {
    "text": "Another mini battle!",
    "start": 346.628,
    "duration": 1.924
  },
  {
    "text": "Another mini battle.",
    "start": 348.552,
    "duration": 0.968
  },
  {
    "text": "I thought you\nmentioned something",
    "start": 349.52,
    "duration": 0.8
  },
  {
    "text": "about there being a mini\ntrophy for the winner?",
    "start": 350.32,
    "duration": 1.958
  },
  {
    "text": "So you guys know, it\ntook him 0.2 seconds",
    "start": 352.278,
    "duration": 1.902
  },
  {
    "text": "to ask for his trophy after\nthe watermelon-kick punt win.",
    "start": 354.18,
    "duration": 2.63
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, congratulations\nCoby Cotton, there it is.",
    "start": 356.81,
    "duration": 3.149
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you, Tyler,\nit means the world.",
    "start": 359.959,
    "duration": 1.541
  },
  {
    "text": "He's a great guy.",
    "start": 361.5,
    "duration": 0.73
  },
  {
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, it's\neveryone's favorite time,",
    "start": 366.59,
    "duration": 2.22
  },
  {
    "text": "the Big Shot.",
    "start": 368.81,
    "duration": 2.479
  },
  {
    "text": "Typically, we go to\nthe top of the stadium,",
    "start": 371.289,
    "duration": 1.791
  },
  {
    "text": "like section 300, 400 is max.",
    "start": 373.08,
    "duration": 2.85
  },
  {
    "text": "This is like a stadium\non top of a stadium.",
    "start": 375.93,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "And I don't like it.",
    "start": 377.95,
    "duration": 1.237
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's do this.",
    "start": 379.187,
    "duration": 0.583
  },
  {
    "text": "I do not like heights.",
    "start": 385.14,
    "duration": 1.33
  },
  {
    "text": "Take a look folks,\ntake a look at that.",
    "start": 386.47,
    "duration": 2.14
