  {
    "text": "That.",
    "start": 388.61,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Woo.",
    "start": 391.09,
    "duration": 0.619
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, here we go.",
    "start": 391.709,
    "duration": 0.916
  },
  {
    "text": "This is the Rooftop\nSuper Bowl Swisher.",
    "start": 396.34,
    "duration": 1.89
  },
  {
    "text": "[CHEERING]",
    "start": 404.704,
    "duration": 1.992
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah!",
    "start": 406.696,
    "duration": 2.488
  },
  {
    "text": "Woo!",
    "start": 409.184,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": "We're so high!",
    "start": 413.668,
    "duration": 1.462
  },
  {
    "text": "I get to go down,\nthat's why I'm excited.",
    "start": 415.13,
    "duration": 1.825
  },
  {
    "text": "[CHEERING]",
    "start": 425.393,
    "duration": 2.051
  },
  {
    "text": "'Atta baby!",
    "start": 427.444,
    "duration": 0.678
  },
  {
    "text": "I am going to take all\nthe credit for that one.",
    "start": 428.122,
    "duration": 1.958
  },
  {
    "text": "I told him to\nthrow it, you know?",
    "start": 430.08,
    "duration": 1.374
  },
  {
    "text": "East-west wind, so anyway, it's\nkind of my shot, pretty cool.",
    "start": 431.454,
    "duration": 3.546
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks Gar.",
    "start": 435.0,
    "duration": 0.904
  },
  {
    "text": "What's up, guys?",
    "start": 435.904,
    "duration": 0.666
